short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Lets you share your browsing activity when taking an online exam on ProctorExam - https://www.proctorexam.com

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension enables browser activity sharing for the ProctorExam online proctoring platform. Browser activity can only be shared by starting an online proctored exam on your-institution.proctorexam.com, so you don't need to worry about sharing unintentionally.

By installing this extension, you are giving ProctorExam permission to view your browsing activity during an online proctored examination.

FOR TEST TAKERS:

Once you have installed the extension, please go back to the system check and refresh the page, or complete : 'STEP 1 - complete the system check' in the email you have received about your exam. 

If you have any difficulties downloading this extension, please contact our chat support. It will be available for you during step 1. Alternatively you can contact our chat support at https://www.proctorexam.com.

FOR DEVELOPERS:

Any questions related to our extension, please contact us using the ‘contact the publisher’ button on the right of this screen. Alternatively you can reach out to your account manager for further assistance.
